   <p>
    <br/>
    This sign is similar in meaning to the gesture of "thumbs down" used in the 
"Hearing World."
    <br/>
    "Thumbs down" (or THUMB-DOWN) is often used for situations such as:
    <br/>
    Signer A: PAST-NIGHT MOVIE? YOU ENJOY?
    <br/>
    Signer B: THUMB-DOWN
    <br/>
    Also thumbs down is good for meanings for that such as:
    <br/>
    "not a fan"
    <br/>
    "meh" / "not good"
    <br/>
    "boo"
    <br/>
    "nix"
